Greeedy algorithum works on two thing
-->Mathematical proof
--->Intution
--->
to apply a greedy Algorithum we make and proof it using mathematic
-->finding the max of two elment in an array 
   |---> claim : sort the element and find the last two element and get the sum to get the required anserwer
   |---> then GA =(GA)n + (GA)n-1
         and OA = (OA)n + (OA)p
   |-->Mathematical Proof:
       |--> GA - OA = ((GA)n - (GA)n-1) - ((OA)n -(OA)p))
       |--> GA - OA = ((GA)n-1  - (OA)p
      
        
